assignment2

Class Feedback

  • java.lang.Object
    • assignment2.Feedback

  • public class Feedback
extends java.lang.Object
    Feedback class for storing the feedback. For Mastermind, the feedback consists of the number of black pegs and the number of white pegs. Black pegs signify correct colors in the correct position. White pegs signify correct colors in the wrong position.
    Author:
    Brad Gray and Jake George, EE422C
